---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Drawnix handles your personal data, including email collection, analytics, and user submissions.">

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 14, 2025<br />
      <strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 14, 2025</p>

      <p>
        Drawnix ("we", "our", or "us") operates 
        <a href="https://drawnixstudio.com">https://drawnixstudio.com</a> and is committed to protecting your privacy. 
        This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your choices regarding your data.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>A. Information You Provide Voluntarily</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Email address when you subscribe to our newsletter or request resources.</li>
        <li>User submissions for "Spotlight Friday", including digital product links, descriptions, or related info.</li>
        <li>Poll responses or idea suggestions when you vote on or suggest digital product ideas.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>B. Automatically Collected Data</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Google Analytics data (IP address, browser type, device info, pages visited, etc.).</li>
        <li>Cookies, including those from embedded YouTube videos.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send requested resources or updates (only if you opt in).</li>
        <li>To feature selected user submissions (with consent).</li>
        <li>To analyze website traffic and improve content.</li>
        <li>To determine popular product ideas via polls.</li>
        <li>To process purchases (if applicable).</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>3. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Email collection and user submissions.</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> Site analytics and basic functionality.</li>
        <li><strong>Contract:</strong> For processing payments or revenue-share agreements.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent your data. We may share it with trusted services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>MailerLite</strong> – Email list management.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> – Site usage analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong> – Payment processing (if/when used).</li>
        <li><strong>YouTube</strong> – Embedded video functionality.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        We use cookies for performance and embedded media. You can control cookie settings via your browser. 
        If you're in the EU/UK, we may show a cookie consent banner.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Emails: Retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion.</li>
        <li>Submissions: Retained for the duration of campaigns or features.</li>
        <li>Analytics: Anonymized data may be retained for performance tracking.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data.</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from emails at any time.</li>
        <li>Contact us with privacy-related concerns: <u><a href="/contact">contact page</a></u>.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>EU/UK users may lodge complaints with a data authority if needed.</p>

      <hr />

      <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect your data, but no online system is ever 100% secure. 
        You use the site at your own risk.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        We may link to other websites. Their privacy practices are beyond our control, so please review their policies separately.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with a revised “Last Updated” date.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, reach out to us by filling out the form on our
        <u><a href="/contact">contact page</a></u>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
